window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Drizzt returns to Luskan, and the Realms will never be the same!</p> <p>The Arcane Brotherhood has long held the city of Luskan in their power, but when corruption eats away at their ranks, Captain Deudermont comes to the rescue of a city that has become a safe haven for the Sword Coast's most dangerous pirates. But rescuing a city from itself may not be as easy as Deudermont thinks, and when Drizzt can't talk him out of it, he'll be forced to help.</p> <p>Drizzt is back in action again, and bringing more changes to the <b>Forgotten Realms</b> setting. This all new hardcover adventure will keep Drizzt fans guessing the whole way, with edge-of-your-seat action and plot twists that even the most casual listener of the <b>Forgotten Realms</b> novel line can't afford to miss.</p> <p>TM &amp; Â©2023 Wizards of the Coast LLC</p>"; 
